            <note xml:id="foot.f1">The date range is conjectured from the dates of publication of most of the reviews of <ref target="../bibliographies/bibl_7951.xml" resp="#mjhawkins"><hi rend="italic">Variation</hi></ref> (see n. 2, below).</note>
