            <note xml:id="foot.f3">CD refers to his provisional hypothesis of heredity, pangenesis, presented in chapter 27 of <ref target="../bibliographies/bibl_7951.xml" resp="#mjhawkins"><hi rend="italic">Variation</hi></ref> (<ref target="../bibliographies/bibl_7951.xml" resp="#mjhawkins"><hi rend="italic">Variation</hi></ref> 2: 357–404).</note>
